---
// No necesitamos importar lucide-react, usaremos SVG estáticos
---

<footer class="bg-gray-900 dark:bg-black text-white transition-colors duration-300">
  <!-- Newsletter Section -->
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gateway-blue to-gateway-blue-dark dark:from-gateway-blue-light dark:to-gateway-blue py-12">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl mb-4 text-white">¡Mantente Conectado!</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Suscríbete a nuestro newsletter para recibir las últimas noticias, promociones y tips para aprender inglés.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
          <input
            type="email"
            placeholder="Tu correo electrónico"
            class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 rounded-lg bg-white text-gray-900 border-0 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-white focus:outline-none"
          />
          <button class="bg-white text-gateway-blue hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-gateway-blue-dark dark:bg-gray-100 dark:text-gateway-blue dark:hover:bg-white transition-colors duration-300 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg border-0 shadow-md font-medium">
            Suscribirse
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Footer Content -->
  <div class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
        
        <!-- Company Info -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-1">
          <h3 class="text-2xl mb-6 text-white dark:text-gray-100">Gateway Corporation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Transformando vidas a través de la educación del inglés. Más de 15 años de experiencia 
            ofreciendo programas de calidad mundial en Ecuador.
          </p>
          
          <!-- Contact Info -->
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400">
              <svg class="mr-3 text-gateway-blue-light" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>+593 2 123 4567</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400">
              <svg class="mr-3 text-gateway-blue-light" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
                <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
              </svg>
              <span>info@gatewaycorp.edu</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400">
              <svg class="mr-3 text-gateway-blue-light" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path>
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
              </svg>
              <span>Quito, Ecuador</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Quick Links -->
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg mb-6 text-white dark:text-gray-100">Enlaces Rápidos</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li>
              <a href="#programs" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Programas
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#promotions" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Promociones
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#testimonials" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Testimonios
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#student-system" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Sistema Estudiantil
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#contact" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Contacto
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Programs -->
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg mb-6 text-white dark:text-gray-100">Nuestros Programas</h4>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li>
              <a href="#programs" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Gateway English Primaria
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#programs" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Gateway Academic Secundaria
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#programs" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Gateway Intensivo Adultos
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#programs" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Gateway Summer Camp
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#programs" class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
                Gateway Corporate
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Social Media & Hours -->
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-lg mb-6 text-white dark:text-gray-100">Síguenos</h4>
          <div class="flex space-x-4 mb-8">
            <a href="#" class="bg-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 p-3 rounded-full hover:bg-gateway-blue hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-gateway-blue-light transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-110" aria-label="Facebook">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="bg-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 p-3 rounded-full hover:bg-gateway-blue hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-gateway-blue-light transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-110" aria-label="Instagram">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect>
                <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path>
                <line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="bg-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 p-3 rounded-full hover:bg-gateway-blue hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-gateway-blue-light transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-110" aria-label="Twitter">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M23 3a10.9 10.9 0 0 1-3.14 1.53 4.48 4.48 0 0 0-7.86 3v1A10.66 10.66 0 0 1 3 4s-4 9 5 13a11.64 11.64 0 0 1-7 2c9 5 20 0 20-11.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 0-.08-.83A7.72 7.72 0 0 0 23 3z"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
            <a href="#" class="bg-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 p-3 rounded-full hover:bg-gateway-blue hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-gateway-blue-light transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-110" aria-label="YouTube">
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M22.54 6.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.94-2C18.88 4 12 4 12 4s-6.88 0-8.6.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.94 2A29 29 0 0 0 1 11.75a29 29 0 0 0 .46 5.33A2.78 2.78 0 0 0 3.4 19c1.72.46 8.6.46 8.6.46s6.88 0 8.6-.46a2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.94-2 29 29 0 0 0 .46-5.25 29 29 0 0 0-.46-5.33z"></path>
                <polygon points="9.75,15.02 15.5,11.75 9.75,8.48"></polygon>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h5 class="mb-3 text-white dark:text-gray-100">Horarios de Atención</h5>
            <div class="text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1 text-sm">
              <p>Lunes - Viernes: 8:00 AM - 8:00 PM</p>
              <p>Sábados: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
              <p>Domingos: Cerrado</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom Bar -->
  <div class="border-t border-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 py-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
        <div class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 text-sm mb-4 md:mb-0">
          © 2024 Gateway Corporation. Todos los derechos reservados.
        </div>
        <div class="flex space-x-6 text-sm">
          <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
            Política de Privacidad
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 hover:text-gateway-blue-light dark:hover:text-gateway-blue transition-colors duration-200">
